T1  - Spontaneous pregnancy and its outcome after human menopausal gonadotropin/human chorionic gonadotropin-induced pregnancy.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/s0015-0282(16)45851-6
A1  - Ben-Rafael, Z
