T1  - [Use of the clomiphene test for evaluation of the functional state of the hypothalamus-pituitary gland-ovarian system in ovarian hyperandrogenia].
T2  - Ispol'zovanie klomifenovoi proby dlia kharakteristiki funktsional'nogo sostoianiia sistemy gipotalamus-gipofiz-iaichniki pri ovarial'noi giperandrogenii.
