N2  - A case is presented of bilateral simultaneous tubal pregnancy after ovulation induction with a clomiphene-menotropin combination. Although extremely rare in the general population, the entity of simultaneous pregnancies is far more common with ovulation induction. Care must be taken not to mistake an extrauterine pregnancy for a hyperstimulated ovary.
