N2  - The incidence of galactorrhea in 480 ovulatory females was compared to that in 383 anovulatory females. One percent of the ovulatory and 3.2% of the anovulatory patients had bilateral galactorrhea. The probability (P) of these two groups being from the same population was less than 0.02.
