T1  - Attempts to programme ovulation with exogenous oestrogens and LH-RH analogue.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1136/bmj.2.5970.527
A1  - Zanartu, J
A1  - Rosner, J M
A1  - Guiloff, E
