T1  - Polycystic ovarian disease, maturation arrest of spermiogenesis, and Klinefelter's syndrome in siblings of a family with familial hirsutism.
A1  - Cohen, P N
A1  - Givens, J R
A1  - Wiser, W L
A1  - Wilroy, R S
A1  - Summitt, R L
